ssed for BFHI compliance?','No',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(25,'q_25','Is there a recognized mechanism for community-based support to mothers for BFHI (Step 10)?','No',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(26,'q_26','Is breastfeeding education incorporated into the training of health professionals?','Yes',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(27,'q_27','If yes, provide details.','MIYCN Training package has a module on Breastfeeding.',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(28,'q_28','Are the Ten Steps covered in pre-service training of health professionals?','Yes',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(29,'q_29','If yes provide details.','It is part of the curriculum of all the health care professionals(Doctors, Nurses, CHWs)',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(30,'q_30','What continuing education courses are provided on the Ten Steps?','MIYCN',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(31,'q_31','What is being done to incorporate the Ten Steps more fully into pre-service training?','Engagement with National Universities Commision and professional bodies on curriculum update.',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(32,'q_32','Are there joint training programs that combine the Ten Steps to Successful Breastfeeding with other relevant health competencies, such as maternal health or newborn or PNC training packages, and I...','Yes',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(33,'q_33','Does the country have a national pool of trainers on the BFHI that has been active in the last two years?','Yes',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(34,'q_34','How many healthcare providers have been trained on BFHI in the last two years?','2219',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(35,'q_35','Is there a system in place to ensure continuous training on breastfeeding support? ','Yes',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(36,'q_36','Does the training cover all Ten Steps to Successful Breastfeeding and the International Code of Marketing of Breast-milk Substitutes?','Yes',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(37,'q_37','Are the BFHI quality statements and measures incorporated in national MNCH QoC strategies and documents?','Yes',0,1,'Nigeria','na'),(38,'q_38','Are the national or sub-national BFHI or BF f